{"tid":1797592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「廚房佬」昨尖沙咀被捕　警指藏「 19 厘米利刀」","createTime":"2019-12-25T14:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T01:57:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":199,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"d44f91a420903ee3a25d1b9ad3465d589cc912c2","tid":1797592,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:34:45.000Z","msg":"昨日平安夜香港多區爆發衝突，曾於理大為抗爭者煮食、人稱「廚房佬」的施漢恆，昨日亦在尖沙咀被捕。警方證實昨日拘捕一名39歲姓施男子，指他涉嫌公眾地方行為不檢、阻礙警務人員執行職務及藏有攻擊性武器，並稱在他身上檢獲一把 19 厘米長的刀。<br />\n<br />\n警方證實，昨日（24日）晚上約9 時，警員巡經尖沙咀廣東道及梳士巴利道交界時，截查一名可疑男子，該名男子拒絕合作及出示身份證明文件，並高聲呼叫。警方遂將他拘捕，並於他身上檢獲一把約 19 厘米長的刀。<br />\n<br />\n警方指該名39歲姓施男子涉嫌公眾地方行為不檢、阻礙警務人員執行職務及藏有攻擊性武器被捕，現正被扣留調查，案件交由油尖警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n「廚房佬」施漢恆早前因身體不適及情緒問題住院一個月，12 月 20 日出院。昨日尖沙咀晚上再有人聚集和警方衝突，期間施漢恆被警方拘捕。施漢恆原訂今日在「光榮冰室」派免費聖誕大餐，如今因為被扣留調查而無法現身。不過聖誕大餐今晚繼續舉行，現場有數百市民到場支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF%E4%BD%AC-%E6%98%A8%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F-19-%E5%8E%98%E7%B1%B3%E5%88%A9%E5%88%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BB%259A%25E6%2588%25BF%25E4%25BD%25AC-%25E6%2598%25A8%25E5%25B0%2596%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%2592%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F-19-%25E5%258E%2598%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2588%2580%2F&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=73cdb313\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BB%259A%25E6%2588%25BF%25E4%25BD%25AC-%25E6%2598%25A8%25E5%25B0%2596%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%2592%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F-19-%25E5%258E%2598%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2588%2580%2F&h=45c2f5be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF%E4%BD%AC-%E6%98%A8%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F-19-%E5%8E%98%E7%B1%B3%E5%88%A9%E5%88%80/</a>"},{"pid":"495723adb0fb634f41431143e78f028bf64e4304","tid":1797592,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200f8c7024cc3cd90a7185374416596cb5fdcf9a","tid":1797592,"uid":187493,"like":199,"dislike":2,"score":197,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"廚房佬隨身帶刀好出奇呀？"},{"pid":"0882641aa61710f3e97bcc8e101cbdd15332b73d","tid":1797592,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afbda4d53794226d152bc0abd82d73de5aac204","tid":1797592,"uid":55563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80453e7a26755399406b6ad6f9849ebb3ea03791","tid":1797592,"uid":113000,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:37:44.000Z","msg":"廚師唔帶得刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75